==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outbalance
<hw>Out*bal"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To outweight;
to exceed in weight or effect.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let dull Ajax bear away my right⟦br⟧
When all his days <qex>outbalance</qex> this one night.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outbar</ent>⟦br⟧
